                 "storage":  {
                                 "value":  "\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"045ebadc-025d-438b-953c-01817724a6bf\"\u003eCorrection of product contract\u003c/ac:inline-comment-marker\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"5e73adc4-4209-4147-97e3-2b85d7fc8c3f\"\u003eGeneral rule for correction:\u003c/ac:inline-comment-marker\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOld billing data shouldn\u0026rsquo;t be unmarked after correction process is completed\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp /\u003e\u003cp\u003eCorrection flow should always use new price component settings connected to contract version respective for period from invoice billing data\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eCorrection process Should Include only PODs which are from old invoice\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBilling group configuration should be taken from old invoice and should ignore current billing group settings\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis configuration is needed only for Separate invoice for each POD (slots)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf i\u003cac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"7219509e-7477-4e9c-ad37-ad566ea14b73\"\u003envoice slot is splitted because of product/customer change and all such invoices aren\u0027t in the list of correction invoices - should return \u003c/ac:inline-comment-marker\u003ean error\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGeneral note:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"417f2eda-0744-4ac1-bc24-3218a5291162\"\u003eConsider slot settings from old invoice price component setting and run billing only for this invoice slot\u003c/ac:inline-comment-marker\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor all correction flows should be skipped interim deduction and compensation flows from standard\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eBilling run configuration from old invoice should be taken and correction flow should be started only for that types of application models\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCorrection for electricity invoice\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eTake billing data period from old invoice and start \u0027with electricity invoice\u0027 flow\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInvoice date\u003c/strong\u003e for with electricity invoice flow should be taken from old invoice\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePeriodic/one time\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eTake \u003cstrong\u003einvoice date\u003c/strong\u003e from old invoice and start periodic/one time flow\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOnly Price change checked\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eOld billing data from old invoice should be used\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"63cfc81c-61a8-4fad-a82a-ee53b65784d9\"\u003eSame invoice slot should be used\u003c/ac:inline-comment-marker\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOnly volumes checked (POD reversal)\u0026nbsp; - \u003cac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"8c719f78-c209-46b6-83c8-6eb5ea06074f\"\u003ereceived billing data isn\u0027t only correction type\u003c/ac:inline-comment-marker\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eCalculate correction process only for PODs and price components for which new billing data is received and ignore all old billing data records from old invoice\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eAll price components which are different from scales/by settlement should be ignored in correction\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eReversal invoices should be created only for this PODs and price components for which new billing data is received;\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"d399b582-9788-431e-9808-b77b3c5e7c33\"\u003eUse only new billing data by profile; \u003c/ac:inline-comment-marker\u003eif two or more billing data is used in old invoice and only one new profile is uploaded  -  in this case will be an error; all billing Data by profile should be uploaded in order to correct\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOnly volumes checked (only correction) - received billing data is only correction type\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor PODs for which only billing data for scales is received - only correction type \u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eCheck if POD is slp and price component in current configuration or old invocie configuration contains at least one price component with by Settlement period - \u003cstrong\u003estart only volume (POD reversal) flow\u003c/strong\u003e; Find latest standard/override +corrections from old invoice and newly received correction record and run standard flow with this normalized scales data\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;For PODs for which only billing data for scales is received - only correction type and contract is combined\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnlock billing data by profile which was used for old invoice and calculate difference \u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(7,71,166);\"\u003e\u003cu\u003e(áááááááááá¡ á¨áááá®ááááá¨á áá£ ááá á¢á á¡á¥ááááá¡ á¥áá áá¥á¨ááá áááááááá á¯ááá áááááª ááá­áá áááá ááá¡áááááááá á¯ááá áá áá áááá áªáá ááááá á á áááááááá¬ááá á¥áá áá¥á¨áá áááááá¡á¨á)  )\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp /\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf for POD billing data by scale with correction type is received and price component is only by scales shouldn\u0027t create any reversal invoice and calculate this invoice and generate debit/credit note only based on this correction record\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf for this pod price component has restriction should go to \u003cstrong\u003eonly volume (POD reversal) flow\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice change and volumes change flow\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eOld volumes and New volumes which aren\u0027t invoiced should be taken based on old invoice billing data period (which shouldn\u0027t include different profiles from old invoice) and should recalculate\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eFirstly to create full reversal invoice and then to recalculate\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnlock old volumes and also use new ones for correction flow\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor each billing data by profile from old invoice take respective (header dates, profile type, dimension, should exact match) latest billing data by profile version\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse this period to find contract version and run standard billing for this contract version\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp /\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eService contract correction flow\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eBased on invoice date from old invoice find service contract version and standard flow/generate final debit or credit note, not invoice\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp /\u003e\u003cp /\u003e\u003cp /\u003e\u003cp /\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eService/goods order\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eSkip from correction process\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCorrection Offsetting\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eDirect offsetting should start from newly received receivable to old liability and then to start automatic offsetting\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cp\u003eStart automatic offsetting\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e",
